headline.print_headline: Program by Alphabet Beats a Human Professional at Go
headline.main: Program by Alphabet Beats a Human Professional at Go

snippet: DeepMind, a research organization, said that a program combining two separate algorithms had soundly defeated a high-ranking professional Go player.
lead_paragraph: DeepMind, a research organization, said that a program combining two separate algorithms had soundly defeated a high-ranking professional Go player.
